
when ever u get this error:
  unable to modify the permissions and get the error  read only filesystem.
    check for mount point using umount command.
    dmesg | grep filesystem(ext): This command will execute all kernel issues.
		ext3_abort called.
		EXT3-fs error (device sdb1): ext3_remount: Abort forced by user
